title: EPISODE 273: Biden FBI Raids Pro-Life Activist in Rural Pennsylvania
description:
MASSIVE MONDAY UPDATES! A Santa Fe District Attorney said Alec Baldwin is likely to face charges as a special prosecutor has been appointed. Conservative populist Giorgia Meloni is set to be Italy’s first female Prime Minister; Poso analyzes how Meloni was able to win the people over by exposing the WEF agenda to be anti-family and anti-human. Defense attorneys in the Oath Keeper case exercised their right to due process when they filed a motion to reveal the identities of the federal informants - the right to face your accuser. In rural Pennsylvania, President Biden’s FBI thugs raided a pro-life activist’s home in front of the activist’s seven children.



Here’s your Daily dose of Human Events with @JackPosobiec
